Modern Vibrant Refresh: Big Lake, MN Interior Transformation

In this Big Lake, MN residence, we provided a bold color transition to bring a warm, modern energy to the living spaces. We moved from a dated beige and green palette to a dynamic two-tone orange design, featuring Fame Orange (the deeper, bold accent on the central fireplace/TV wall) and Sweet Orange (the softer, lighter shade on the surrounding walls). In the bathroom, we neutralized a heavy orange with a crisp, bright gray, providing a clean and calming aesthetic. This project highlights how strategic color choices and precision lines can completely redefine the mood and character of a home.

